# Copy to .env.local and edit. Both .env.local and .env*.local are gitignored.
#
# PRISM_WORKSPACE: absolute path to the directory holding your prism
# workspace (_meta/, _resumes/, apps/, postings/, .state/).
#
# Defaults to ~/prism-workspace if unset. Create that directory (or set
# this to your existing one) before running `npm run dev`.

# PRISM_WORKSPACE=/Users/you/prism-workspace
